00:00:05.809 --> 00:00:08.665
As part of a promotion, each
customer will also receive

00:00:08.665 --> 00:00:11.068
an additional discount
on the marked sale price

00:00:11.068 --> 00:00:12.844
at the cash register.

00:00:12.844 --> 00:00:17.244
