00:00:27.947 --> 00:00:29.503
we're gonna assume
everything is in dollars.

00:00:29.503 --> 00:00:31.627
It's on sale for 30 percent off.

00:00:31.627 --> 00:00:34.878
Well if you're 30 percent off
that means it's gonna cost

00:00:34.878 --> 00:00:37.396
70 percent of the regular price.

00:00:37.396 --> 00:00:40.578
So let's put 70 percent of 40.

00:00:40.578 --> 00:00:43.457
So let's multiply that times
0.7, which is the same thing

00:00:43.457 --> 00:00:44.885
as 70 percent.

00:00:44.885 --> 00:00:49.192
40 times 0.7, that's going to be equal to

00:00:49.192 --> 00:00:52.892
28, $28.

00:00:52.892 --> 00:00:55.887
Right? Yeah, seven times four is 28.

00:00:55.887 --> 00:00:59.985
