All right, so it's going to be $28

00:01:01.924 --> 00:01:03.665
would just be the 30% off.

00:01:03.665 --> 00:01:06.684
But the final price of
the jeans was $22.40.

00:01:06.684 --> 00:01:07.949
What additional discount

00:01:07.949 --> 00:01:10.748
