00:01:10.748 --> 00:01:13.347
Well to figure that
out, we can just divide.

00:01:13.347 --> 00:01:16.468
We can say, what fraction of 28 is 22.40.

00:01:16.468 --> 00:01:21.468
22.40 divided by, divided by 28.

00:01:21.491 --> 00:01:23.985
Well this is going to
be equal to, let's see,

00:01:23.985 --> 00:01:27.131
28, and actually you could even rule out,

00:01:27.131 --> 00:01:29.674
well I'll do the
arithmetic right over here.

00:01:29.674 --> 00:01:33.648
